com.cerner.beadledom.jaxrs

Class ErrorBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.beadledom.jaxrs.ErrorBody

  • public class ErrorBody
extends Object
    A one-time stream of the response entity body representing an error.

    Like the Response.readEntity(java.lang.Class<T>) methods this provides one-time use access to the body. Once the body has been consumed by one of the methods on this class, additional calls to any of the methods will lead to an exception.

    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    John Leacox
